These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower, begonia
There 3 different types of food: peas, peach, asparagus
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, accountant, firefighter
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, alhambra, cain
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the firefighter##1
2. the engineer is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is between the person eating peach and the person eating asparagus##2
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
5. the firefighter is the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Flower         | sunflower | dahlia   | begonia   |
| Food   | peach     | peas | asparagus |
| Job   | firefighter  | engineer    | accountant      |
| Cigar     | alhambra     | fonseca      | cain |

