.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, fuchsia, chestnut
House: cottage, art-deco, craftsman
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, skateboard, bike
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, zinnia, poppy
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the craftsman house##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is the person driving the bike##1
4. the person who likes ivory is the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person who growsorchid is between the art-deco house and the person who likes chestnut##2
6. the person who likes chestnut is the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Color          | fuchsia  | ivory     | chestnut     |
| House   | art-deco     | craftsman     | cottage      |
| Transport   | bike  | skateboard | ship |
| Flower           | poppy | orchid     | zinnia       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, british, egyptian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, siglo, davidoff
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, electronic, metal
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, roller, ship
1. the game-smoker is on the left of the fan metal##1
2. the person driving the scooter is between the davidoff-smoker and the fan metal##2
3. the american is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the roller is the british##1
5. the person driving the scooter is the fan electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality          | american  | egyptian     | british     |
| Cigar           | davidoff | game  | siglo   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | electronic    | metal |
| Transport           | ship     | scooter | roller |

