.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daffodil, daisy
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, canasta
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, january, september
House: wooden, art-deco, cottage
1. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is between the person playing backgammon and the person who's birthday is in july##2
4. the person who growsdaffodil is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Flower    | zinnia       | daisy  | daffodil   |
| Game     | backgammon    | canasta  | mah-jongg |
| Birthday     | january   | september | july        |
| House   | cottage | wooden     | art-deco      |

