The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, june, december
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, horror, action
House: futuristic, palace, townhouse
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the futuristic house is between the person watching action movies and the person who's birthday is in december##2
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the palace house##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the futuristic house is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Cigar          | aristoff    | old-henry     | montecristo      |
| Birthday         | april | june | december |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | horror       | sports       |
| House           | palace     | futuristic       | townhouse     |

