.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
3 different games are played: go, whist, domino
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, blue, orange
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, roller, subway
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, ice-hockey, rugby
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person playing domino is the person who likes brown##1
3. the person driving the roller is between the person playing whist and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
4. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
5. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Game          | whist | go | domino    |
| Color         | blue | orange      | brown |
| Transport   | airplane   | roller     | subway        |
| Sport           | handball      | rugby       | ice-hockey      |

