City: hamburg, hannover, liverpool
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the fan soul is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person traveling to hamburg##2
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
5. the fan soul is between the fan funk and the aristoff-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Game          | mah-jongg      | backgammon   | whist |
| Music-Genre         | electronic | soul | funk |
| Cigar   | aristoff      | prince | montecristo   |
| City     | liverpool         | hannover  | hamburg       |

