.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, fishing, board-games
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, february, september
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, black, ebony
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, electrician, dressmaker
1. the dressmaker is between the person who likes black and the person who likes ebony##2
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes orange is on the left of the electrician##1
6. the electrician is the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks      | fishing | board-games     |
| Birthday          | february   | july      | september     |
| Color   | ebony  | orange      | black |
| Job     | software-developer | dressmaker        | electrician     |

