.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, cabbage, lettuce
3 different pets are kept: bird, snake, cat
House: craftsman, art-deco, modern
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, filmmaking, magic-tricks
1. the person eating cabbage is the owner of the cat##1
2. the art-deco house is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
5. the person eating cabbage is between the owner of the snake and the art-deco house##2
6. the craftsman house is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Food      | cucumber | cabbage      | lettuce            |
| Pet           | bird | cat | snake |
| House   | art-deco     | modern        | craftsman         |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | woodworking    | magic-tricks        |

