.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, van, taxi
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, snowboarding, biathlon
City: venice, boston, miami
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, card-games, baking
1. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Transport      | van    | taxi          | helicopter |
| Sport          | biathlon | snowboarding           | rowing        |
| City           | boston | miami | venice         |
| Hobby   | chess    | baking    | card-games      |

