.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-15::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, water-polo, sailing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, romance, adventure
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, manager, firefighter
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, mirinda
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the manager##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person watching adventure movies and the firefighter##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person watching adventure movies and the person who's sport is surfing##2
5. the person watching romance movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Sport          | sailing  | water-polo   | surfing |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | romance     | zombie |
| Job   | social-worker | manager | firefighter   |
| Beverage     | mirinda   | hot-chocolate   | milk      |

