3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
4. the person who growstulip is the person who likes brown##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Birthday       | february | july | april |
| City         | nizza   | marseilles       | edinburgh        |
| Flower       | bellflower | orchid   | tulip         |
| Color   | green    | coral     | brown         |

