There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, fanta, 7up
City: edinburgh, prague, hannover
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, card-games, writing
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person drinking lemonade##2
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person traveling to prague##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Birthday   | may | january  | september     |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta | lemonade |
| City           | edinburgh        | hannover   | prague  |
| Hobby     | writing      | card-games   | cooking |

