The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, dahlia, poppy
House: gothic-revival, palace, art-deco
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, bartender, photographer
1. the bartender is the art-deco house##1
2. the palace house is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
3. the gothic-revival house is between the person playing snooker and the person who growsiris##2
4. the palace house is the photographer##1
5. the engineer is between the person playing monopoly and the palace house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Game      | snooker | mah-jongg     | monopoly        |
| Flower         | dahlia   | poppy | iris |
| House   | palace        | gothic-revival       | art-deco      |
| Job           | photographer           | engineer    | bartender       |

