.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, spanish
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, disco, dubstep
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, water
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, chaman, bongani
1. the colombian is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the fan disco is the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the person drinking tea is the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is the spanish##1
5. the fan dubstep is between the bongani-smoker and the person drinking tea##2
6. the person drinking water is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality        | german      | colombian | spanish |
| Music-Genre         | disco     | dubstep    | soul        |
| Beverage       | tea | water   | soy-milk   |
| Cigar   | aristoff          | chaman     | bongani       |

 